  "body": "## Issue\r\n\r\nInstalling truffle-contract on my machine (which has g++ installed) fails with an error about a Clang-specific flag unknown to g++: “unrecognized command line option '-stdlib=libc++'`”\r\n \r\n\r\n## Steps to Reproduce\r\n\r\n`npm install -g truffle-contract`\r\n\r\n## Actual Results\r\n\r\n` SOLINK_MODULE(target) Release/copied_files.node`\r\n`c++: error: unrecognized command line option '-stdlib=libc++'`\r\n\r\n## Workaround\r\n\r\n`CC=clang CXX=clang++ npm install -g truffle-contract`\r\n\r\n## Environment\r\n\r\n* Operating System: MacOS 10.13.6 17G7024\r\n* Compilers:\r\n```\r\n19> which -a c++\r\n/usr/local/bin/c++\r\n/usr/bin/c++\r\n\r\n23> /usr/local/bin/c++ --version\r\n\r\nc++ (Homebrew GCC 8.3.0) 8.3.0\r\nCopyright (C) 2018 Free Software Foundation, Inc.\r\n…\r\n24> /usr/bin/c++ --version\r\n\r\nApple LLVM version 10.0.0 (clang-1000.11.45.5)\r\n…\r\n```\r\n",
